            VLLM[provider-vllm]
            Groq[provider-groq]
            Fireworks[provider-fireworks]
            Together[provider-togetherai]
            Azure[provider-azure-openai]
        end
    end

    subgraph Management["modelrouter-admin"]
        Admin["router-admin<br/>CQRS command side"]
    end

    subgraph UI["modelrouter-dashboard"]
        Dashboard[router-dashboard]
    end

    Obs["router-observability<br/>OTel · Prometheus · Langfuse"]

    Redis[(Redis)]
    Postgres[(PostgreSQL)]
    Kafka[(Kafka)]

    SDKJava --> Ingress
    SDKAndroid --> Ingress
    RESTClient --> Ingress

    Ingress --> Security
    Security --> PolicyEngine
    PolicyEngine --> Planner
    Planner --> Runtime
    Runtime --> SPI
    Runtime --> Cache
    SPI --> OpenAI & Anthropic & Gemini & Ollama & Baseten & VLLM & Groq & Fireworks & Together & Azure

    Cache --> Redis
    Planner --> Redis

    Admin --> Postgres
    Admin -. policy change events .-> Kafka
    Kafka -. hot reload .-> PolicyEngine
    Runtime -. usage events .-> Kafka

    Dashboard --> Admin
    Dashboard --> Obs

    Runtime -. traces/metrics .-> Obs
    Ingress -. traces/metrics .-> Obs

    OpenAI & Anthropic & Gemini & Groq & Fireworks & Together & Azure -->|HTTPS| ExternalCloud[External Cloud Providers]
    Ollama & VLLM & Baseten -->|local/self-hosted| LocalInference[Local / Self-Hosted Inference]

